<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - কই যাবো | KoyJabo</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="Privacy Policy for KoyJabo (কই যাবো) - Bangladesh's Smart Transport Route Finder. Learn how we protect your data.">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://koyjabo.com/privacy-policy.html">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">

    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <meta name="google-adsense-account" content="ca-pub-6933713424631305">
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-6933713424631305"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #006a4e 0%, #004d38 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #006a4e;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #006a4e;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #004d38;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        ul,
        ol {
            margin-left: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #006a4e;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            background: #004d38;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 106, 78, 0.3);
        }

        .update-date {
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🔒 Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>কই যাবো (KoyJabo) - Bangladesh's Smart Transport Route Finder</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>

            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 26, 2026<br>
                <strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2024
            </div>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>কই যাবো (KoyJabo)</strong>. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring
                a safe online experience.
                This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use
                our website
                <a href="https://koyjabo.com">koyjabo.com</a> and our Progressive Web Application (PWA).
            </p>
            <p>
                Please read this privacy policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this privacy policy,
                please do not access the site or use our services.
            </p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3>2.1 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
            <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information about your device,
                including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URLs, pages viewed,
                    and timestamps</li>
                <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, screen resolution, and browser settings</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Search queries (bus routes, destinations), feature usage patterns, and
                    interaction with the app</li>
                <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Approximate location based on IP address (we do NOT track precise
                    GPS location without your explicit permission)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2.2 Location Information (Optional)</h3>
            <p>
                If you choose to use our "Use My Location" feature, we request access to your device's GPS location
                <strong>only with your explicit consent</strong>.
                This information is used solely to:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Show your current location on the map</li>
                <li>Find nearby bus stops and routes</li>
                <li>Provide turn-by-turn navigation</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Important:</strong> Location data is processed locally on your device and is NOT stored on our
                servers. You can disable location access at any time through your browser or device settings.</p>

            <h3>2.3 Cookies and Local Storage</h3>
            <p>We use cookies and browser local storage to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Remember your preferences (language, theme, favorite routes)</li>
                <li>Enable offline functionality (caching route data)</li>
                <li>Analyze site usage (via Google Analytics - see Section 4)</li>
                <li>Serve personalized advertisements (via Google AdSense - see Section 5)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not work correctly.</p>

            <h3>2.4 Personal Information (Minimal)</h3>
            <p>
                <strong>We do NOT require you to create an account or provide personal information</strong> to use
                KoyJabo. The app works anonymously.
                However, if you contact us via email for support, we may collect:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your name (if provided)</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Message content</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This information is used only to respond to your inquiry and is never shared with third parties.</p>

            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>To Provide Services:</strong> Display bus routes, maps, and transport information based on
                    your search queries</li>
                <li><strong>To Improve User Experience:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to optimize app performance and
                    add new features</li>
                <li><strong>To Enable Offline Access:</strong> Cache route data locally so you can use the app without
                    an internet connection</li>
                <li><strong>To Serve Relevant Ads:</strong> Display advertisements via Google AdSense (which helps keep
                    the app free)</li>
                <li><strong>To Comply with Legal Obligations:</strong> Respond to legal requests or prevent fraudulent
                    activity</li>
            </ol>

            <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect information about you:</p>

            <h3>4.1 Google Analytics</h3>
            <p>
                We use Google Analytics to understand how users interact with our app. Google Analytics collects data
                such as pages visited,
                time spent on the site, and user demographics. This data is anonymized and aggregated.
            </p>
            <p>Learn more: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></p>

            <h3>4.2 Google AdSense</h3>
            <p>
                We display advertisements via Google AdSense to support this free service. Google may use cookies to
                serve ads based on
                your prior visits to our website or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by
                visiting
                <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank">Google Ad Settings</a>.
            </p>
            <p>Learn more: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank">Google
                    AdSense Privacy</a></p>

            <h3>4.3 Google Gemini AI</h3>
            <p>
                Our AI Assistant feature is powered by Google Gemini. When you ask a question, your query (and
                conversation history) is sent to
                Google's servers for processing. Google's privacy policies apply to this data.
            </p>
            <p>Learn more: <a href="https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/terms" target="_blank">Google Gemini Terms</a></p>

            <h3>4.4 Leaflet Maps (OpenStreetMap)</h3>
            <p>
                We use Leaflet and OpenStreetMap to display interactive maps. OpenStreetMap does not track individual
                users but may log
                tile requests (map images) for operational purposes.
            </p>
            <p>Learn more: <a href="https://wiki.osmfoundation.org/wiki/Privacy_Policy" target="_blank">OpenStreetMap
                    Privacy Policy</a></p>

            <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain data for the following periods:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Device/Browser Storage:</strong> Data cached in your browser (e.g., route searches,
                    preferences) remains until you clear your browser cache or uninstall the app</li>
                <li><strong>Server Logs:</strong> Automatically collected log data is retained for up to 90 days for
                    security and analytics purposes</li>
                <li><strong>Support Emails:</strong> Correspondence is retained for up to 2 years for record-keeping
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>6. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We <strong>DO NOT sell, rent, or trade</strong> your personal information. We may share data only in the
                following circumstances:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>With Service Providers:</strong> Google (Analytics, AdSense, Gemini AI) processes data on
                    our behalf</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> If required by law, court order, or government request</li>
                <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> If KoyJabo is acquired or merged, user data may be transferred
                    to the new owner (you will be notified)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>
                KoyJabo is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information from
                children under 13 years of age.
                If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will delete it
                immediately.
            </p>
            <p>
                Parents or guardians who believe their child has provided personal information should contact us at
                <a href="mailto:mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com">mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com</a>.
            </p>

            <h2>8. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
            <p>You have the following rights regarding your data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Access:</strong> Since we don't collect personal accounts, most data is stored locally on
                    your device (you have full access)</li>
                <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Clear your browser cache/cookies to delete locally stored data</li>
                <li><strong>Opt-Out of Location:</strong> Deny location permissions in your browser/device settings</li>
                <li><strong>Opt-Out of Ads:</strong> Use <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
                        target="_blank">Google Ad Settings</a> to manage ad personalization</li>
                <li><strong>Contact Us:</strong> Email us at <a
                        href="mailto:mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com">mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com</a> to request data
                    deletion or ask questions</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information, including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmitted between your device and our servers</li>
                <li>Secure hosting infrastructure (GitHub Pages, Cloudflare CDN)</li>
                <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your
                data,
                we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>

            <h2>10. International Users</h2>
            <p>
                KoyJabo is primarily designed for users in <strong>Bangladesh</strong>. If you access our service from
                outside Bangladesh,
                please be aware that your data may be transferred to and processed in countries with different data
                protection laws.
            </p>
            <p>
                By using KoyJabo, you consent to the transfer of your information to Bangladesh and other countries
                where our service providers operate.
            </p>

            <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal
                requirements.
                We will notify you of significant changes by:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page</li>
                <li>Displaying a prominent notice on our website</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Your continued use of KoyJabo after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated
                Privacy Policy.
            </p>

            <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Mejbaur Bahar Fagun</strong><br>
                Developer & Owner, KoyJabo<br>
                📧 Email: <a href="mailto:mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com">mejbaurbaharfagun@gmail.com</a><br>
                🔗 LinkedIn: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mejbaur/" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/mejbaur</a><br>
                🌐 Website: <a href="https://koyjabo.com">koyjabo.com</a>
            </div>

            <h2>13. Consent</h2>
            <p>
                By using KoyJabo, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
            </p>

            <p class="update-date">
                <strong>Last Reviewed:</strong> January 26, 2026<br>
                This Privacy Policy is effective as of January 1, 2024, and will remain in effect except with respect to
                any changes
                in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page.
            </p>

            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to KoyJabo Home</a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024-2026 KoyJabo (কই যাবো). All rights reserved.</p>
